text: Hans Bredmose (23 August 1888 - 18 December 1958) was a Danish gymnast. He competed in the men's team event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:1958 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
